{"title":"springboot","uid":"4c539d6e180882f90490e79c71481d8f","slug":"后端/Springboot","date":"2020-11-15T12:19:04.000Z","updated":"2022-04-06T09:13:39.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/后端/Springboot.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/springboot.jpeg","content":"<h1 id=\"Redis相关\"><a href=\"#Redis相关\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Redis相关\"></a>Redis相关</h1><p><strong>启动</strong> sudo redis-server &#x2F;etc&#x2F;redis&#x2F;redis.conf</p>\n<p><strong>终止</strong> </p>\n<ol>\n<li>登陆后 shutdown save</li>\n<li>service redis-server stop</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>操作</strong> redis-cli -p 6379 –raw</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>查看List <code>lrange ListName 0 -1</code><br>查看key  <code>keys * </code><br>查看value <code>get KeyName</code></p></blockquote>\n<br/>\n\n<h1 id=\"Springboot-注解\"><a href=\"#Springboot-注解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Springboot 注解\"></a>Springboot 注解</h1><p><code>@ConfigurationProperties(prefix = &quot;xxx&quot;)</code> </p>\n<p>告诉SpringBoot将本类中的所有属性和配置文件中相关的配置进行绑定；<br> prefix &#x3D; “xxx”：注解，其中prefix 指定配置文件里的前缀</p>\n<br/>\n\n<h1 id=\"Spring-Boot-Configuration-Annotation-Processor-not-configured-问题解决\"><a href=\"#Spring-Boot-Configuration-Annotation-Processor-not-configured-问题解决\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Spring Boot Configuration Annotation Processor not configured 问题解决\"></a>Spring Boot Configuration Annotation Processor not configured 问题解决</h1><p><strong>原因</strong></p>\n<p>Spring Boot配置注解执行器没有配置：配置注解执行器配置完成后，当执行类中已经定义了对象和该对象的字段后，在配置文件中对该类赋值时，便会非常方便的弹出提示信息</p>\n<p><strong>解决</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;&#x2F;groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-configuration-processor&lt;&#x2F;artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;optional&gt;true&lt;&#x2F;optional&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;dependency&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h1 id=\"微服务案例\"><a href=\"#微服务案例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"微服务案例\"></a>微服务案例</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8